<div class="title">Mood Is Everything</div>
<div class="substance">Diazepam (Valium)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Mysticide&Exact=1">Mysticide</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Mysticide. "Mood Is Everything: An Experience with Diazepam (Valium) (exp31496)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Nov 14, 2007. erowid.org/exp/31496</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

